# Constraints
1)The system must be accessible through all major web browsers
2)The system must support low-bandwidth connections
3) The system can only have a max of 4h/month downtime
    REQ32
4)You can reach any content within 3 clicks
    REQ37
5)A single login will be required
    REQ38
6)The system will provide an export to commonly used calander formats
    REQ47
7)The system should provide a one click function which will mail all students of the course their grade
    REQ58
8) Administrative constraints
    REQ97-107
